OL,3,C'Gutted': MP promises to help factory
OL,4,Cworkers after closure announcement
OL,6,FAn MP says he is "gutted" hundreds of
OL,7,Fworkers will lose their jobs after the
OL,8,Flargest fibre glass factory in the UK
OL,9,Fannounced its closure - but has
OL,10,Fpromised to help wherever possible.
OL,12,FMore than 250 jobs will be lost when
OL,13,Fthe NEG Nippon Electric Glass Fibre
OL,14,FWorks (EGFU) closes its doors for the
OL,15,Ffinal time at the end of June.
OL,17,FThe future of the site, based at
OL,18,FHindley Green near Wigan, has been in
OL,19,Fdoubt since April, when NEG announced
OL,20,Fthey were looking for a buyer to take
OL,21,Fover their UK branch.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
