OL,3,C'Gutted': MP promises to help factory
OL,4,Cworkers after closure announcement
OL,6,FJosh Simons, Labour's MP for
OL,7,FMakerfield admitted it will be "a
OL,8,Fdifficult few weeks" for those
OL,9,Finvolved.
OL,11,F"It is gutting for Hindley Greeners,"
OL,12,Fhe said. "Its going to be a difficult
OL,13,Ffew days and few weeks, and I know
OL,14,Fthat there are families right across
OL,15,Fmy constituency who are struggling
OL,16,Fmentally and even financially with
OL,17,Fwhat's going to happen next.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
