OL,6,F"And I just want them to know that I'm
OL,7,Fhere, my office is here, the council's
OL,8,Fhere, the college is here, and we will
OL,9,Fall be there tonight and several times
OL,10,Fover the next few days and weeks to
OL,11,Fsupport them."
OL,13,FThe closure was confirmed at a Board
OL,14,Fof Directors meeting on Wednesday 18
OL,15,FJune, where the company's president
OL,16,FAkira Kishimoto announced it would
OL,17,F"cease operations" of their UK
OL,18,Fsubsidiary.
OL,20,FThe President confirmed the site will
OL,21,F"stop its production in late June".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
