OL,3,C'Gutted': MP promises to help factory
OL,4,Cworkers after closure announcement
OL,6,FMr Simons has been involved in ongoing
OL,7,Fnegotiations over recent months to try
OL,8,Fand keep the factory alive, with his
OL,9,Ffrustration with owners Nippon clear.
OL,11,F"I can't tell you how many times over
OL,12,Fthe last three months we thought we'd
OL,13,Fgot a deal over the line," he said.
OL,15,F"It looks like every condition's been
OL,16,Fmet and I've been expecting a call
OL,17,Ffrom the UK CEO or from Japan saying
OL,18,Fthe deals over the line, its going to
OL,19,Fbe OK and then something changes,
OL,20,Fthere's a new condition somewhere.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
