OL,6,F"And what's happened over the last two
OL,7,Fweeks in particular is two deals have
OL,8,Ffallen through that were viable,
OL,9,Fcommercial deals, that the government
OL,10,Fexpressed its support for, the mayor
OL,11,Fof Greater Manchester expressed his
OL,12,Fsupport for, I've expressed support
OL,13,Ffor, but then Nippon changed the terms.
OL,15,F"And I just don't have confidence any
OL,16,Flonger that Nippon is serious about
OL,17,Fdoing a deal."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
