OL,3,C'Gutted': MP promises to help factory
OL,4,Cworkers after closure announcement
OL,6,FJosh Simons said many had worked
OL,7,Ftirelessly to try and get a deal over
OL,8,Fthe line to save the factory, but the
OL,9,FNippon continued to "change the goal
OL,10,Fposts".
OL,12,FThe MP held a special meeting for
OL,13,Fworkers and their families at the site
OL,14,Fat which groups from across the local
OL,15,Farea and the city region came together
OL,16,Fto explore what opportunities there
OL,17,Fmay be for staff in the future.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
