OL,3,C'Gutted': MP promises to help factory
OL,4,Cworkers after closure announcement
OL,6,FHe returned early from Parliament to
OL,7,Fjoin the group aimed at bringing the
OL,8,F'whole borough' together to help the
OL,9,Fworkers and their families.
OL,11,FThe Grove Company, which recently
OL,12,Fhelped redundant Thomas Cooks staff,
OL,13,Fwas just one of the attendees,
OL,14,Falongside Wigan Council support staff,
OL,15,Fand Wigan and Leigh College to discuss
OL,16,Fretraining and education opportunities.
OL,18,F"The evening was full of mixed
OL,19,Femotions," Mr Simons said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
