OL,3,C'Gutted': MP promises to help factory
OL,4,Cworkers after closure announcement
OL,6,F"I wanted to be there to show workers
OL,7,Fthey're not alone and to let them know
OL,8,Fthe support that's available from
OL,9,FWigan Council, Wigan and Leigh
OL,10,FCollege, DWP, and the Growth Company,
OL,11,Fas well as Work Well.
OL,13,F"I know things are going to be hard,
OL,14,Fbut this is a community that will pull
OL,15,Ftogether, and we'll make sure that
OL,16,Feveryone gets what they need.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
