OL,3,C'Gutted': MP promises to help factory
OL,4,Cworkers after closure announcement
OL,6,F"My support for the workers continues
OL,7,Fand in the coming weeks I will be
OL,8,Fhosting a jobs fair. The fight now
OL,9,Fbegins for a new, positive future for
OL,10,Fthis site and the Hindley community
OL,11,Fand I will work tireless to make this
OL,12,Fhappen."
OL,14,FHe added it was not just about
OL,15,Fimmediate actions, but also about
OL,16,Frelaunching former NEG staff in the
OL,17,Ffuture, and said a job fair will also
OL,18,Fbe held in around a month so those who
OL,19,Fwere made redundant get opportunities
OL,20,Ffor retraining and potentially a new
OL,21,Fjob if they want them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
