OL,3,C'Gutted': MP promises to help factory
OL,4,Cworkers after closure announcement
OL,6,FMr Simons says that negotiators met
OL,7,Fall the conditions that were imposed
OL,8,Fby Nippon, but that "the goal posts
OL,9,Fwere moved again and again and again".
OL,11,FBut his hope for the future remains
OL,12,Fundimmed, and together with the union
OL,13,Fand other partners across the town and
OL,14,Fthe city region, he says he is
OL,15,Fdetermined to find a viable future for
OL,16,Fthe site, and for the people who lost
OL,17,Ftheir jobs, and their families:
OL,19,F"We're still at the early stages of
OL,20,Fplanning what's going to come next,"
OL,21,Fhe said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
