OL,3,C'Gutted': MP promises to help factory
OL,4,Cworkers after closure announcement
OL,6,F"But I think the workers on the plant,
OL,7,Fthe GMB who I've been working really
OL,8,Fclosely with know this by now, I'm not
OL,9,Fgoing to let this slip, this is not
OL,10,Fgoing to just drift off into something
OL,11,Fthat takes 5, 10, 15 years to resolve.
OL,13,F"Nippon have decided to close the
OL,14,Fplant, we now need to make sure these
OL,15,Fworkers get a good deal, and a good
OL,16,Fpackage from Nippon, and then we need
OL,17,Fto start work straight away on what
OL,18,Fthe future of this plant looks like."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
